  <Aside>This app is currently in development. Features and design are being improved.</Aside>  
  <p>
    Developed with Laravel 11, this web application is designed to streamline and centralize the operations of a veterinary clinic. It offers a comprehensive suite of features for managing staff, clients, pets, services, and inventory, all within an intuitive and user-friendly interface.
    <!-- <code>114514</code> -->
  </p>
