  <h3 id='veterinary_app_key_features'>Key features</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Dashboard:</span> Visualize key system statistics, including clients, pets, consultations, and appointments, with dynamic charts and graphs.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Role & Permission Management:</span> Implement granular access control for different user types, ensuring secure and organized system administration.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">User Management:</span> Manage system accounts efficiently, including creation, modification, and role assignment.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Employee Positions:</span> Define internal roles such as veterinarians, assistants, and administrators.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Veterinarian Management:</span> Register and monitor medical staff, tracking their activities and responsibilities.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Pet Species:</span> Categorize pets by species, including dogs, cats, rabbits, and more.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Vaccination Tracking:</span> Record and manage vaccines, track general information, and maintain individual pet follow-ups.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Services Management:</span> Organize and manage the services offered by the clinic.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Client Management:</span> Maintain detailed records of pet owners.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Pet Records:</span> Keep comprehensive medical and general information for each pet.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Veterinary Consultations:</span> Document medical history, symptoms, diagnoses, and treatments for pets.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Events & Calendar:</span> Schedule appointments and view them in a calendar format for easy planning.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Inventory Management:</span> Track categories, products, warehouses, stock levels, inventory movements, and suppliers.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Sales Module:</span> Register and manage invoices for products sold to clients.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Multi-language Support:</span> Available in English and Spanish. Choose your preferred language to use the application.
    </li>
    <li>
      <span class="subtitle">Dark Mode: </span> Toggle between light and dark themes for optimal user experience.
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    This application is ideal for veterinary clinics seeking to automate their processes, improve efficiency, and centralize all operations in a single, modern platform.
  </p>
